w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/stardew-valley"><em>《星露谷物语》的</em></a>粉丝们很快就能通过开发商 Eric &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/concernedape">ConcernedApe&#39;Barone</a>和作家 Ryan Novak 编写的官方食谱来烹饪整个季节的美食。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/wholesome-games-are-for-you-and-theyre-here-to-stay-3014776">有益健康的游戏适合您，并且会一直存在</a></strong></li></ul><p>该食谱包含 50 多种受游戏启发的食谱，例如一些村民最喜欢的著名粉红蛋糕，该食谱重点关注时令食材，以体现<em>《星露谷物语</em>》的可持续原则（由<em><a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/stardew-valley-is-getting-a-cookbook-co-authored-by-creator-eric-barone/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PC Gamer</a></em>发现）。虽然有些菜肴是不言自明的，例如农夫午餐或蟹饼，但还是有惊喜的。</p><p>奇怪的面包是其中的特色，考虑到这需要小麦粉、长春花和空蛋黄酱才能在<em>星露谷物语中烘烤它，</em>巴罗和诺瓦克会为现实世界的版本选择什么还是个谜。</p><p>农业模拟游戏的长期粉丝也会兴奋地发现这本食谱包含原创插图以及所有小吃和甜点的照片。它<a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/1984862057?tag=georiot-trd-21&amp;ascsubtag=pcg-gb-7539761874179771000-20&amp;geniuslink=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可以在 2024 年 4 月 16 日发布之前通过亚马逊预订</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3484318" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3484318" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3484318 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-2.jpg" alt="《星露谷物语》的截图显示了浅绿色草地上的一座深色石屋。一名玩家拿着一个盘子，盘子中央有一条鱼。图片来源：ConcernedApe" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/stardew-valley-cookbook-coming-very-soon-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484318" class="wp-caption-text"> 《星露谷物语》图片来源：ConcernedApe</figcaption></figure><p><em>星露谷物语</em>并不是唯一一款拥有自己的专用食谱来复制虚拟世界中制作的饭菜的游戏。 Chelsea Monroe-Cassel 根据<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/world-of-warcraft"><em>《魔兽世界》</em></a>撰写了三本烹饪书，为玩家提供烹饪艾泽拉斯主题美食的机会。</p><p>蒂博·维拉诺瓦 (Thibaud Villanova) 是一位 YouTuber，也被称为 Gastroogeek，他是<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/assassins-creed">《刺客信条</a>：烹饪法典》的</em>幕后主脑。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/official-assassins-creed-recipe-book-lets-fans-can-cook-through-the-ages-3008891">“十个完整菜单”，</a>包括“Masyaf Moutabel、Davenport Homestead Soup、波士顿苹果派、殖民地凉拌卷心菜、Meringues Mirabeau、Rooks&#39; Bread Pudding”等菜肴。</p><p>然而，Barone 参与<em>星露谷</em>物语官方食谱的事实很有趣。他的参与程度尚不清楚，但创作者正在平衡<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/stardew-valley-update-1-6-will-add-secrets-and-a-new-festival-3469789"><em>《星露谷物语》</em>的支持</a>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/haunted-chocolatier">《闹鬼巧克力》</a></em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/concernedape-taking-break-from-haunted-chocolatier-for-stardew-valley-update-1-6-3431557">开发</a>。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，大型多人在线游戏<em>Palia</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/palia-is-shaping-up-to-be-the-cosiest-mmo-around-3474780">在其冒险世界中提供了更加轻松的体验</a>- 在这个世界中，你“更有可能在厨房里烧伤拇指，而不是遭遇可怕的结局”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/stardew-valley-official-cookbook-includes-pink-cake-and-strange-buns-3484301">《星露谷物语》后的官方食谱包括粉红蛋糕和奇怪的面包，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
