8.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/primavera-barcelona-2023-peru-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/primavera-barcelona-2023-peru-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/primavera-barcelona-2023-peru-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/primavera">Primavera Sound</a>宣布今年将在秘鲁首次亮相，标志着该音乐节的最新扩展。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/primavera-sound-barcelona-festival-2023-review-3452075">2023 年巴塞罗那 Primavera Sound 回顾：值得大喊大叫的回归</a></strong></li></ul><p>该音乐节还在巴塞罗那、布宜诺斯艾利斯、圣保罗、波哥大等地举办，并将于 11 月在其最新的南美洲地区首次亮相。</p><p> Primavera Sound 将于 11 月 22 日、12 月 2 日、7 日和 8 日在利马举行，届时<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cure">The Cure</a> 、Bad Gyal、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pet-shop-boys">Pet Shop Boys</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-religion">Bad Religion</a>将成为头条新闻。目前的阵容中还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/just-mustard">Just Mustard</a>和 The Cure 的常规开场表演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-twilight-sad">《暮光之城》</a> 。</p><p> Primavera Sound 在他们的社交媒体上分享了这一新消息，并表示<a href="http://primaverasound.com/en/lima" target="_blank" rel="noopener">即将推出更多售票信息。</a></p><p> The Cure 将于即将在圣保罗、布宜诺斯艾利斯、波哥大和亚松森这四个即将举行的南美音乐节上亮相，这是他们十年来首次在南美演出，作为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-add-more-dates-to-2023-north-american-tour-3426669">失落之歌”世界巡演的</a>一部分。 </p><figure id="attachment_3423034" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3423034" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3423034" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/the-cure-robert-smith-new-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="《治愈》的罗伯特·史密斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/the-cure-robert-smith-new-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/the-cure-robert-smith-new-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/the-cure-robert-smith-new-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/the-cure-robert-smith-new-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/the-cure-robert-smith-new-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/the-cure-robert-smith-new-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3423034" class="wp-caption-text"> 《治愈》的罗伯特·史密斯。图片来源：Shlomi Pinto/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-will-not-return-to-madrid-in-2024-3471900">Primavera Sound 证实该音乐节明年不会重返马德里</a>。</p><p>虽然这个由西班牙创办的音乐节自 2001 年以来一直在巴塞罗那举办，但今年是第一次成为双场地活动，两个地点的演出阵容相同。</p><p>然而，在首届音乐节出现诸多问题后，组织者宣布明年该音乐节将不会在西班牙首都举行。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvpcpzXO4j3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 