-news/bruce-springsteen-forced-miss-american-29730786" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《镜报</em></a>》）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3466097" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3466097" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3466097" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bruce-Springsteen-header-review.jpg" alt="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀在伦敦评论" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bruce-Springsteen-header-review.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bruce-Springsteen-header-review-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bruce-Springsteen-header-review-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bruce-Springsteen-header-review-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bruce-Springsteen-header-review-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bruce-Springsteen-header-review-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3466097" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-announce-2023-us-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3267506">目前正在进行的美国巡演</a>于 2 月 1 日在佛罗里达州开始，这也是斯普林斯汀和 E Street Band 自 2019 年以来首次一起巡演。继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-announce-2023-uk-tour-dates-3269015">英国、爱尔兰和欧盟的一系列演出后</a>，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-announce-more-support-acts-for-london-bst-hyde-park-show-buy-tickets-3456906">在伦敦的头条站BST 海德公园</a>——这位音乐家于 8 月 9 日返回美国进行另一场演出。</p><p>本月，The Boss 在芝加哥瑞格利球场 (Wrigley Field) 举行了他在美国的首场演出，他用了 44 首歌曲列表中的最后一首歌来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-pays-tribute-to-robbie-robertson-us-tour-footage-setlist-3481118">向乐队吉他手兼创作型歌手罗比·罗伯逊 (Robbie Robertson) 致敬，罗比·罗伯逊</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-band-robbie-robertson-has-died-aged-80-3480702">于当天早些时候宣布去世。</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-cancels-two-us-shows-after-being-taken-ill-3484313">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀因“生病”而取消两场美国演出的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
