ww.nme.com/news/music/loona-hyunjin-yeojin-vivi-gowon-hyeju-debut-loossemble-3475425">准备以新组合 Loossemble 的身份首次亮相</a>。成员伊夫<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/loona-yves-meeting-with-agencies-future-solo-3465456">尚未与新经纪公司签约</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/court-rules-favour-ex-loona-member-chuu-contract-lawsuit-blockberry-creative-3484285">法院在针对经纪公司 Blockberry Creative 的合同诉讼中做出了有利于前 LOONA 成员 Chuu 的裁决，该裁决</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
